    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When a creature that you can see within 30 feet of you takes damage, you can use take a Reaction to cause your Arcane Ward to absorb that damage. If this damage reduces the ward to 0 Hit Points, the warded creature takes any remaining damage. If that creature has any Resistances or Vulnerabilities, apply them before reducing the ward's Hit Points.</p><section id=\"secret-OFHX0GaoHBasYkBx\" class=\"secret\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The <strong>Project Ward</strong> activity uses your reaction and can be used to reduce the Ward's uses (\"HP\").</p></section>",
